data.description: A beautiful rambling ranch, on a stunning piece of land, in a well established neighborhood. Whats new? New compressor & condenser for the hvac. A new deck, water filter,under-counter lighting in the kitchen, high end Ecobee thermostat, 8 foot privacy fence & bathroom vanity w. soft close drawers. New fenced in area and dog door for your fur babies. New gutters, a new roof on the home and shed. The shed has a fresh red & white coat of paint. This home boasts 4 bedrooms or 3 bedrooms and a den. The kitchen & walk in pantry are a chefs dream. The kitchen is the hub of the home, with 3 living areas surrounding it. A cozy hearth room w. built in bookcases, a living room and a den. A cozy covered front porch. Watch the deer stroll through the yard. In the spring watch the perennials bloom. Gather on the new deck & enjoy s'mores by the fire pit. Owners are moving cross country so this home is an all in package deal with high end fridge in the kitchen and garage, a John Deere & high end washer and dryer w. pedestals and hand crafted workbench w. casters on it that can be used in the garage or the shed. This home is move in ready! Sellers offering a one point buy down on a mortgage.
